  "texts": [
    "• The study propose a new PCES technique that involves two types of encoding to process data leading to improved encoding that further enhances model's performance in terms of achieving accurate results.",
    "The structure of this paper is as follows: Sect. 2 provides an overview of the relevant literature on the subject at hand.",
    "The methodologies employed in the current study are described in Sect. 3.",
    "Furthermore, Sects.",
    "4 and 5 present the results and discussion, and Sect. 6 concludes the paper."
  ]
